Detailed Description

template<class charType_t__>
class fsdict::Hash< charType_t__ >

Hash provides a hash table which stores and finds c-strings.

The class is designed to be used for hashing suso-strings for fast traversable dictionaries -

Inserted strings are stored in a buffer here in Hash, the hash table stores pointers into that buffer.

Author:
Uli Reffle, <uli@reffle.de>
